OL,3,CCommunity rallies to arrange a visit
OL,4,Cfrom Santa to terminally ill Jacob
OL,6,FA ten-year-old boy who has a life-
OL,7,Flimiting illness has been meeting
OL,8,FSanta after his community responded to
OL,9,Fan appeal from the family.
OL,11,FJacob Rimmer from Bootle, in
OL,12,FMerseyside, has a rare genetic
OL,13,Fcondition and his family are preparing
OL,14,Fto take him to Claire House Childrens'
OL,15,FHospice.
OL,17,FBut before he goes, Jacob's mum Gemma
OL,18,Fasked the local community for a home
OL,19,Fvisit from Father Christmas...and soon
OL,20,Fenough Father Christmas was on his way.
