OL,3,CCommunity rallies to arrange a visit
OL,4,Cfrom Santa to terminally ill Jacob
OL,6,FGemma and dad Kevin, and his two
OL,7,Fbrothers, are focusing on making every
OL,8,Fmoment count and creating cherished
OL,9,Ffinal memories.
OL,11,FGemma said: "We asked on the community
OL,12,FFacebook page for Santa, and everyone
OL,13,Fcame together to arrange for Jacob and
OL,14,Fhis brothers to have that magical
OL,15,Fmemory.
OL,17,F"It was amazing, like I've never seen,
OL,18,Fboth the community and everyone has
OL,19,Fcome together to support us as a
OL,20,Ffamily."
