OL,3,CCommunity rallies to arrange a visit
OL,4,Cfrom Santa to terminally ill Jacob
OL,6,FJacob suffers from a rare and severe
OL,7,Fmetabolic disorder, non-ketotic
OL,8,Fhyperglycinemia (NKH), which has
OL,9,Fcaused his health to deteriorate
OL,10,Frapidly over the past year.
OL,12,FHe also battles epilepsy and cerebral
OL,13,Fpalsy.
OL,15,FAs the family prepares for the
OL,16,Fdifficult transition of moving Jacob
OL,17,Finto Claire House Children's Hospice,
OL,18,Fthey say the outpouring of support has
OL,19,Fbeen a huge comfort to them.
